A floating window.

A full-screen window that obscures all other windows.

A hidden window.

Annotation

Property Documentation

DeviceRGBColor org.pdfclown.documents.multimedia.MediaScreenParameters.Viability.BackgroundColor [get, set]

Gets/Sets the background color for the rectangle in which the media is being played.

This color is used if the media object does not entirely cover the rectangle or if it has transparent sections.

double org.pdfclown.documents.multimedia.MediaScreenParameters.Viability.BackgroundOpacity [get, set]

Gets/Sets the opacity of the background color.

Returns:
A number in the range 0 to 1, where 0 means full transparency and 1 full opacity.
